Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.34,0:01:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命中！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.18,0:01:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后1个！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.53,0:01:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没子弹了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:01:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.05,0:02:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.53,0:02:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？我还活着？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.09,0:02:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.31,0:04:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底打算把我愚弄到什么地步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用Tharsis出击 给我准备Sky Carrier！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,且慢 库鲁迪欧伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎赫巴姆伯爵 为什么要阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.15,0:04:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你说让我活捉他的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他发现你追击他而改变目的地的话 事情反而不好办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道那家伙到底要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.98,0:04:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为那家伙是为了什么而使用谒见室的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他是间谍 就一定会有同伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.59,0:04:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会从上空追踪他的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.04,0:04:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的增援？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.41,0:04:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他阻止了对我们的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.44,0:04:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内讧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.73,0:04:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.92,0:04:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许只是在争夺猎物而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样都好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:05:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那是敌人的敌人 就算不是同伴也有利用价值
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是哪一族敢来妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这片土地已经是我费米安的领土了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:16.45,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(716,655)}Femieanne
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.23,0:05:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不允许你在我的领地上肆意妄为
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 我的眷属们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布提斯的手指…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:17.69,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(567,655)}Botis
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:17.69,tips,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注：布提斯 所罗门72柱魔神中排第17位的魔神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.25,0:06:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞠户上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞠户上尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休穆雷！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧我 休穆雷！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞠户…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.53,0:06:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休穆雷！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就救你出来 休穆雷！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全打不中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.31,0:06:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它拉开了距离 也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制塔！打开船坞式机库！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Mustang-22的请求！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:06:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.55,0:06:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,界冢的弟弟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:06:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捂住耳朵！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 请捂住耳朵！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:13.03,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Share me your madness that you keep in
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:16.73,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Show that you're scared like me Thus we are teens
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:19.13,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wash my hands of that for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:22.22,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sell myself for this hopeless loop
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.93,0:08:29.72,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,May I have seen your face somewhere sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:31.36,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You freeze my blood and spine
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:32.80,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So freak me out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:35.02,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like a look in a mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.23,0:08:36.96,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Face my Doppelgäger
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.17,0:08:40.07,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How 'bout you? Aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.44,0:08:45.38,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Beware of attentions, entourages and mates
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.53,0:08:47.99,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are what you do
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.74,0:08:53.31,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Depress your metions, ain't got to be a bighead
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.61,0:08:56.79,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are what you fool
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.96,0:08:57.72,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right now
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.82,0:08:59.67,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Burn your soul, neck or nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:02.80,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Burn it out 'til you're losing your reason
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.00,0:09:05.53,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forget the stoned reason to drive it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:07.54,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just to scribe your existence
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:09.57,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not a crime, your insistence
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:12.91,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Die another day
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:13.51,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So do I
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:15.67,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Burn my soul, all to nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:19.01,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Burn it out, let me charge in your advance
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:21.63,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm watching for the chance to beat it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.80,0:09:23.61,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though my body's shaking
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:25.60,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it all, deadly bumping
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.80,0:09:28.59,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cuz you make me feel
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.80,0:09:30.35,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Breathless
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.78,0:08:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐藏的船坞？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.78,0:08:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.86,0:08:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能动！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.84,0:08:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船体呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.75,0:08:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉勉强强…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.63,0:08:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 已经开始进水了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲入前方的船坞里去！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.84,0:08:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全…全速前进！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.68,0:08:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我说…伊奈帆!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mustang-11！我们也跟上吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.89,0:09:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿奈 你自作主张打算做什么…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.60,0:09:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪姐你呢 船的护卫要怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.67,0:09:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机枪扫射！目标 门闸上方的岩石！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.52,0:09:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.95,0:09:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算做什么…橙色的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.04,0:09:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我们去干掉那架三头六臂机体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本扬陆城既将进入可扫描日本列岛的区域
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.08,0:09:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要进入了扫描区域
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就立刻搜索斯雷因·托罗亚特所夺取的那架Sky Carrier
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟拉姆公主其实还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是亲眼见证的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.69,0:10:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎赫巴姆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经发现了那架机体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它现在在日本列岛西南的种子岛上空
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.83,0:10:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像正在和费米安伯爵的重甲骑兵Hellas交战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.32,0:10:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.46,0:10:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在种子岛？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从来没听说过种子岛上有这样的基地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.03,0:10:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 抓紧时间退舰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.88,0:10:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.92,0:10:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧 鞠户上尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.35,0:10:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别挤！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽可能不要吸入烟雾！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.54,0:10:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优先让非战斗人员去避难
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.91,0:10:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧接着是伤兵！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:10:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人都不要落下！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.81,0:10:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.35,0:11:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭阳前辈！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.67,0:11:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mustang小队呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,韵子他们不在甲板上！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.23,0:11:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们还在外面战斗着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.90,0:11:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让我们有时间逃走 在外面充当诱饵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.27,0:11:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命中！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.23,0:11:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 右3密尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.15,0:11:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要攻击强袭舰就必须打碎岩石
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想提升威力就有必要先提升速度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火箭想要加速 必然需要一定的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离一长 只要角度稍有偏差
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准就会出现巨大的偏差
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4点钟方向出现敌机！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它正朝着这边前进
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.78,0:11:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.91,0:12:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星的攻击机会保护我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.34,0:12:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事啊!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.43,0:12:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪姐 直接去攻击敌人的重甲骑兵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊？不可能赢得了那种东西的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.39,0:12:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.69,0:12:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许只是虚有其表而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,韵子 手枪借我一用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.11,0:12:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第11、12区域已确认退舰完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第8区域的退舰工作也结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来全员就都齐了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.76,0:12:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我们也赶紧离开这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和Mustang小队取得联络吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能祈祷他们平安无事了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.01,0:12:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马格巴丽吉舰长！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.93,0:12:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见咲 不是让你带着难民去避难吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.95,0:13:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经让他们暂时到前面的货仓里避难了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.93,0:13:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有件东西想让舰长看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的错吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为我来了地球吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.54,0:13:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.51,0:13:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我没来 就不会发生暗杀事件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战争就不会发生…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们也不会有这种残酷遭遇…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.38,0:13:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记住 对这些人而言 火星人都是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.05,0:13:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也毫无头绪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里到底是用来做什么的设施啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:13:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公…公主殿下！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…火星的重甲骑兵…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.63,0:14:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是陨石坑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.77,0:14:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落到这里的陨石并不只有一块
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.65,0:14:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中一块撞击在海岸形成了海湾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.68,0:14:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一块就落在了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这架机体就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 这就是15年前的恶梦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为Heavens Fall已经把他们全部抹杀了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还真是感动的再会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是说这家伙被俘获了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 是为了隐藏这个事实
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞠户上尉所写的种子岛报告才会石沉大海的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.30,0:14:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的就这么简单吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.11,0:14:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马格巴丽吉舰长！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那儿！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.99,0:15:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.46,0:15:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橙色的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.65,0:15:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 阿奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚刚开始 那台三头六臂就一直待在那里没有动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.87,0:15:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在用同样的手段进行着攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那家伙的武器肯定只有那东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.21,0:15:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你们掩护我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.58,0:15:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 阿奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.18,0:15:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奈帆！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.19,0:15:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在开玩笑吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开启接触回路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.48,0:15:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们长话短说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那边的装备还剩下多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榴弹炮还剩下20发左右
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.95,0:16:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.28,0:16:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HE弹还剩下9发 我身上就只有这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿奈 快回来！那是火星的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 雪姐 一会儿再和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hellas的拳头会通过巨大分子化来增强自身强度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.94,0:16:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什么样的子弹都无法破坏它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.78,0:16:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 有个拳头已经被破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概它的手指活动的时候分子构造会变回原状
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将安定装置的信号传到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:26.73,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(508,655)}stabilizer
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的规格可是不一样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓 我会进行解析的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.20,0:16:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它来了 蝙蝠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.14,0:16:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝙蝠？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:38.07,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unknown soldier lying on the floor
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:40.43,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Explosions forever
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:44.42,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now you take me away from danger
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:47.93,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We had always covered up your face
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:50.30,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Out there who will watch your back?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:54.33,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't know if I can stay here
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.71,0:16:56.10,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Game over
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.27,0:16:59.45,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now we hate our brothers
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.77,0:17:03.29,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No longer can move my feet
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.44,0:17:04.11,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it's
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:05.84,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Keep on keeping on
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.97,0:17:08.08,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And it's I just wanna know
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:10.88,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inside it's I don't want to know
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.08,0:17:14.22,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Over head they fly high it's going
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:15.94,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On and on and on
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.12,0:17:20.98,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will we oversee the smile of love and peace for everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.19,0:17:22.99,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can be sure
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.17,0:17:24.73,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back again
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.10,0:17:53.72,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it's
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:55.32,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Keep on keeping on
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:57.84,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And it's I just wanna know
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:18:00.33,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inside it's I don't want to know
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.54,0:18:03.74,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Over head they fly high it's going
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.92,0:18:05.43,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On and on and on
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.65,0:18:10.61,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will we oversee the smile of love and peace for everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.77,0:18:12.43,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can be sure
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:14.60,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back again
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:26.07,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I remember a long time ago
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:28.59,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will be there for you and please wait for me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:30.88,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh you must believe me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:33.80,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Better you believe your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:38.74,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will be there for you and please wait for me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.92,0:18:41.25,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh you must believe me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.48,0:18:44.17,INEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Better you believe your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩拉克斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:41.00,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(621,655)}Marax
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:41.00,tips,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}注：摩拉克斯 所罗门72柱魔神中排名第21位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.61,0:16:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.59,0:16:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子还是一样爱乱来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.01,0:16:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们继续前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放着他不管可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.86,0:16:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 那孩子每次乱来的结果基本上都是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.69,0:16:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.03,0:17:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一架 从后方跟紧它！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.41,0:17:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果攻击后方无装甲的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以打到它的引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后方又出现了2机
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方向175 沿着海岸线来飞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪姐 能听到我说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我呼之即来挥之即去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方向保持不变！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布提斯…摩拉克斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:38.13,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(530,655)}Botis
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:38.13,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(697,655)}Marax
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.42,0:17:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗诺比 …哈帕斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.42,0:17:40.39,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(544,655)}Ronove
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.42,0:17:40.39,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(701,655)}Halphas
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳姆…拜恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:42.55,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(565,655)}Raum
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:42.55,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(678,655)}Vine
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.82,0:17:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢伤害我的孩子们…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时攻击哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.31,0:17:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.45,0:17:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就拿出我的杀手锏！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.69,0:18:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.03,0:18:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.18,0:18:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.39,0:18:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它拉开了距离 开始加速了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用狙击打偏它的轨道！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.73,0:18:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么大的体型用步枪是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.71,0:18:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在挂着你 机体太沉了躲不开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我把你们撞散
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它来了 蝙蝠！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.43,0:18:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我闭嘴 橙色的家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然躲开了?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.12,0:18:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让机体失速下降了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.88,0:18:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉不起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样的手段对我可行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.26,0:18:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.92,0:19:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞空艇？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是战舰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.28,0:19:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟拉姆公主！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.61,0:19:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有Aldnoah的地球人为什么会驾驶着这样的战舰！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.98,0:20:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12点钟方向敌机接近
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是碰撞路线！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.38,0:20:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的地球人！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.74,0:20:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请准备应对冲击！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.54,0:20:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 还没结束！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.54,0:20:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的火星人都是我父亲的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.27,0:20:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们成功了呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到你了 亚瑟拉姆公主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.66,0:20:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 你为什么还在找她？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.80,0:21:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道公主还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.16,0:21:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这话是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我和公主见一面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.26,0:21:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先回答我的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.99,0:21:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…你想利用公主吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.68,0:21:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我要利用她 你有意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.29,0:21:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.73,0:21:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的敌人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.81,0:21:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.36,0:21:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.05,0:22:11.05,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“二人的邂逅”
